The Spring-o-Bot Framework is a Java Framework to control iRobot Create robots
via the Open Interface.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

In order to use the Spring-o-Bot Framework you need:

 * Java SE 1.6 (Lower versions may be ok too but have not been tested):
   http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/index.html

 * Java Communications 3.0 API:
   http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/index-jsp-141752.html

 * Or the RXTX serial package for Java:
   http://www.cloudhopper.com/opensource/rxtx/

 * An iRobot Create connected to your PC via the serial port (or with the
   optional USB cable):
   http://www.irobot.com/create

